 |
Booking History
```

---

## Benefits

- Provides clear understanding of application workflow.
- Improves user experience planning.
- Helps developers understand system navigation.
- Useful for testing and validation.

---

## Technologies Involved

- React.js
- Express.js
- Node.js
- MongoDB
- Axios
- JWT Authentication

---

## Outcome

The User Flow illustrates the complete booking lifecycle from registration to payment completion, ensuring a smooth and user-friendly experience within the UCAB Cab Booking System.

